name: Seth Meyers

I’d say, ‘Mother, father, how am I gonna get home?’ And they’d just laugh because the subway was so safe. And as the doors would close and the train was rolling away, I’d see them high five each other, the happiest I had ever seen them because of how safe the subway was. And then I’d ride the rails for days and days until I’d find my way home, and they’d be so excited, they’d say, ‘Dear God! What are you doing here?’ And I’d say, ‘Mother and father, I knew you were worried, and good news, the subway is safe.’ And they’d break down crying tears of joy. Because of how safe the subway was.'” seth meyers
